OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTrump challenges $454m     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpenalty in civil fraud case
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Donald Trump is appealing against a New
OL,6, York judge's ruling that he must pay   
OL,7, $454m (#360m) in penalties and interest
OL,8, in a civil fraud case.                 
OL,10,FThis month's judgement was $355m, but  
OL,11,Fthe amount has soared with interest,   
OL,12,Fwhich will keep accruing by at least   
OL,13,F$112,000 per day.                      
OL,15,FNew York Attorney General Letitia James
OL,16,Fhas said if Mr Trump does not pay, she 
OL,17,Fwill seek to seize some of his assets. 
OL,19,FHe was found to have inflated property 
OL,20,Fvalues to obtain better loan terms.    
